      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a helpful analogy, but I'm more worried about the \"hidden\" risks. The clause mentions \"any and all losses\" and \"deficiencies.\" Are there specific ways this could bite me unexpectedly if I'm not careful? Like, are there any \"sneaky\" ways this liability could expand beyond just a simple mistake I made?",
